dct_title_s: State of New Jersey, Board of Commerce and Navigation, Map showing new water line on Barnegat Bay Between Deauville Beach and Mantoloking, Ocean County
dct_description_sm: This is a riparian survey map with information on the water line along Barnegat Bay between Deauville Beach and Mantoloking. It also shows major roads and some unlabeled property lots.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
